OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a cloudy morning
OL,6,Fwith a few spots of light rain
OL,7,Fpossible. Dry and mostly cloudy in the
OL,8,Fafternoon but some bright or sunny
OL,9,Fintervals breaking through, especially
OL,10,Fin the southeast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will be a dry and mostly
OL,13,Fcloudy evening, though a few late
OL,14,Fsunny spells are possible, mainly in
OL,15,Fthe southeast. Overnight, conditions
OL,16,Fwill remain dry and largely cloudy.
OL,17,
OL,18,CTuesday:FAnother largely dry and
OL,19,Fcloudy day with a few bright or sunny
OL,20,Fintervals breaking through .
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
