OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,6,Flargely dry and settled few days with
OL,7,Fthe odd spot of rain possible at
OL,8,Ftimes. Cloudy at times but still
OL,9,Fplenty of bright or sunny spells on
OL,10,Foffer.
